    feature is non-breaking but it is recommended to use the new variables
  * (variables) change --text-color to --base-color
  * (border) change b-{color} to bc-{{color}}
  * (border) set border-color as a variable
  * (grid) drop webkit-fill-available from minvh
  * drop support for IE and dead browser versions
  * remove depreciated styles

